summary: A very large redguard style house for player and followers, with a little dungeon.
descriptionHtml:
A very large, maybe too large redguard style house for player and followers, with a little dungeon.
It was just a test for a future quest mod but it works, and it\'s fun, so why not.
Location : Go to Solitude docks and look for a ship named \"sand rose\". There is a map marker. Good trip.
Necromancians in the mine bottom are not leveled, very dangerous for low level npc\'s so, be careful, or equip one of the protective items i set somewhere in the place.
Required other mods : None.
Issues. send me a message if you have any problems.
author: Leucippe
